messages.content: My babies are in there. Oh, my God, I'm so scared.
Okay. Can you tell me what happened?
My husband's in the van, and it wouldn't stop. I saw him.
Okay. Is the van in park now?
Can somebody check under the van?
No, nobody can get to her. I don't hear anything.
Where exactly are you in relation to the pit stop?
The cop's there. The cop is there.
Do you see the officers? I want you to wave them down.
My name is Nicole. My babies are in there. Oh, my God. It was totally an accident.
Yeah, they are. Can I go, please?
Okay, I'm going to let you go.
